casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jeffrey David KAHL.
No. D-2780.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 9, 2014.
Jeffrey David Kahl, of Nottingham, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
